ARTICLE.TITLE: Mayor Cranley says Dennard 'needs to resign’ if allegations against her are true
ARTICLE.TEXT: Councilman Greg Landsman released a statement on Wednesday: “There is no dimension of this that isn’t awful and sad. What we have to do for residents and taxpayers and everyone we serve is to focus on the work, their phone calls, their emails, and the issues that they bring before us. I am going to make sure we stay focused on that work and on getting things done. People need to know that their government is still working for them. The only reasonable outcome here is that we have 9 members of council that show up every day and are fully capable of doing their job. Every day, completely focused.”
